Privacy Policy for Font Changer Chrome Extension

This Privacy Policy explains how the Font Changer Chrome extension ("Extension") collects, uses, and discloses information from users. By installing or using the Extension, you consent to the collection, use, and disclosure of your information as described in this policy.

Data Collection and Use
The Extension does not collect any personal or sensitive user data. However, the Extension may collect anonymous usage data, such as the number of times the Extension is used or the types of websites where the Extension is used. This data is collected solely for the purpose of improving the functionality and performance of the Extension and is not used for any other purpose.

Data Disclosure
The Extension does not disclose any user data to third parties. However, anonymous usage data may be shared with trusted third-party service providers who assist us in analyzing usage data and improving the Extension's performance.

Data Security and Retention
The Extension takes reasonable measures to protect user data from unauthorized access or disclosure. However, no data transmission over the internet or any wireless network can be guaranteed to be 100% secure. The Extension retains anonymous usage data for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes for which it was collected.

Data Access and Correction
Users can access and correct any anonymous usage data collected by the Extension by contacting us at [insert contact email address]. Users can also request that their anonymous usage data be deleted by contacting us at the same email address.

Changes to this Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes to this policy will be posted to the Chrome Web Store listing for the Extension and will be effective immediately upon posting.

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or the Extension's data collection practices, please contact us at [insert contact email address].

By posting this Privacy Policy to the Chrome Web Store Developer Dashboard, users of the Font Changer Chrome extension can easily access it and understand how their data is being handled.
